<div class="mb-20 md:flex md:gap-20 lg:mb-96">
  <h2 class="text-blue-dark font-georgia mb-4 md:w-1/3">ABOUT</h2> 
  <p class="lg:text-2xl lg:w-1/2 xl:w-1/3">
    We call Kelowna home and seek to make it a place where everyone can thrive.  We advocate for cities of all sizes to be safe, livable, and inviting. Kelowna’s issues of affordability and traffic congestion can only be solved by replacing Kelowna’s post-war pattern of development, the Suburban Experiment, with a pattern of development that is financially strong and resilient. We work to elevate local government to be the highest level of collaboration for people working together in a place, not merely the lowest level in a hierarchy of governments.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="mb-24 lg:mb-96">
  <div about="section">
    <h3 about="title" class="text-blue-dark font-georgia mb-4 md:w-1/3 lg:hidden">5 PRIORITY CAMPAIGNS</h3> 
    <ul about="list" class="flex flex-col gap-4 mb-4 lg:flex-nowrap lg:overflow-x-hidden lg:mb-20 lg:flex-row">
      <li about="item" class="border border-blue flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-lg p-4 min-h-96 md:min-w-96 hidden lg:block xl:min-w-128 2xl:min-w-192">
        <h3 class=" whitespace-nowrap text-blue-dark font-georgia mb-4 md:w-1/3 ">5 PRIORITY CAMPAIGNS</h3> 
      </li>
      <% campaigns.each do |campaign| %>
        <li about="item" class="bg-whitesmoke flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-lg p-4 min-h-96 md:min-w-96 lg:w-96 xl:min-w-128 2xl:min-w-192">
          <h3 class="text-blue-dark font-georgia"><%= campaign[:title] %></h3> 
          <div>
            <%= image_tag campaign[:img], :class => "about-image h-56 bottom-0 rounded-lg w-full object-cover md:h-full " %>
          </div>
          <p ><%= campaign[:description] %></p>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
      <%= button_to "MORE ABOUT STRONG TOWNS", "https://www.strongtowns.org/about", method: "get", class: "transition duration-300 hover:bg-blue-dark hover:text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg text-blue-dark border border-blue-dark" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
